@Jenna 
Exactly. 

I thought SDS was more militant vs being self-described as a 'peace org.'.....but TBH I didn't follow news closely all the time when I was young.

@Dave 

You don’t say in which platform you’re solving, but I’d bet that if you go to Settings, you’ll see a toggle for Show Timer. 

At least that’s what I see on my iPhone app.

@Steve L 

I put SANAA in my pocket, but I guess the pocket had a hole in it, so I had to guess a few letters for SANAA/NADU crossing before I got the right one.

If someone could put the emu in a pocket that does not have a hole in it until this comment gets published, I would appreciate it.

@Helen Wright 
Don't the Britidh have cheddar with apple pie?

Thought I heard that years ago.

@Jim 

And for the record I did finish 3% below my average.

Once again, I apologize for this, but it must be done.  If I leave just the single sentence comment above, which would be my preference, there is a good chance it will be caught in the emu filter and never see the light of day.  Of course much worse things happen in this world, but when you simply want to communicate, and get stifled at almost every turn, it can be annoying.  In conclusion, I hope every one has a stellar weekend, and may all the clues that misdirect lead you to your happy place.

